title: Sydney Talks about Why She Was on Dr. Phil
description: Sydney usually comes on the show to do "This Week on Campus" but this time she tells us all about why she was on Dr. Phil.   It involves a big social media convention scandal that happened in 2018 that Sydney worked for and she spills all the tea.
